Package: stocksTimeSeries
Title: Time Series Forecasting for Daily Equity Closing Prices
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Marvis", "Osazuwa", email = "marvis.osazuwa@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An end-to-end R analysis package for univariate time series
    forecasting of daily equity closing prices. Implements data loading and
    validation, exploratory analysis, log and difference transformations,
    stationarity testing (ADF, KPSS), candidate model fitting (ARIMA, ETS,
    naive baseline), residual diagnostics, and accuracy evaluation, all
    exposed through a reproducible pipeline and standalone driver scripts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
